    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the<strong> cucumber & carrot salad</strong> between the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>Thai-style coconut free range chicken</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>chopped chilli</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and <strong>chopped roasted peanuts</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
